A ''' script''' was used by the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] on their [[Klegger Corp Mining Facility/Legends|base]] on [[Mustafar/Legends|Mustafar]]. It was used in a warning during the [[Duel on Mustafar/Legends|Duel on Mustafar]] between [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] when they accidentally turned the shields off, allowing the lava to damage the base.<ref name="ROTS">{{Film|III}}</ref>

